root: ^“Don’t ever intrude again. You and that boring ass of yours.”
^The light faded. Or rather it is you who are fading. You, emerging from nothingness, and will soon be vanished back into nothingness. Your familiar nothingness, where nothing is sharp.
^Nothing hurts or scratches or leaves any trail of blood.
^Because nothing really has any power No. All is safe and powerless and harmless and innocuous in the nothingness.
